---

Test data from Keycloak realm (imported via order-forge-realm.json):

- Supplier Admin user: username "supplier-admin" (or your chosen email), role: SupplierAdmin
- Sample Customer Organization: "Test Customer Company"
- Sample Customer user: belongs to "Test Customer Company", role: Customer (or CompanyAdmin)

When testing login or features:
- Use these accounts to verify Supplier vs Customer behavior
- SupplierAdmin should see global product management and all orders
- Customer users should only see their own negotiated prices and orders